.TH GUSTD "1" "June 2016" "gustd 0.12"
.SH NAME
gustd \- peer-to-peer network based digital currency
.SH SYNOPSIS
gustd [options] <command> [params]
.TP
gustd [options] help <command> \- Get help for a command
.SH DESCRIPTION
This  manual page documents the gustd program. Gust is an experimental new digital currency that enables anonymous, instant payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Gust uses peer-to-peer technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Gust Core is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.

